1
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
ظآزWandering aloneظآز

2
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
ظآزWalking far by dusk-lit streetsظآز

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
ظآزYour eyes are as cold as cloudsظآز

4
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
ظآزFaintly coming into viewظآز

5
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
ظآزThe city lightsظآز

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
ظآزLit up that single momentظآز

7
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
ظآزI can't hide or stop missing youظآز

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
ظآزI can't forget those momentsظآز

9
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
ظآزLosing youظآز

10
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
ظآزLike the seasons in my memoryظآز

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
ظآزWithout winterظآز

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
ظآزWalking down the long, dark streetظآز

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
ظآزSnow will never fall againظآز

14
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
ظآزOur old story was tornظآز

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
ظآزInto scattered piecesظآز

16
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
ظآزReplaying every single sceneظآز

17
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
ظآزAfter you leftظآز

18
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
ظآزAs if our documentaryظآز

19
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
ظآزLost winterظآز

20
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
ظآزThe breeze speaks of good timesظآز

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
ظآزPure white devotionظآز

22
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
ظآزSend out a letterظآز

23
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
ظآزCarrying my longingظآز

24
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 4=

26
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,120
Lu Tingxiao,

27
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,040
open up.

28
00:01:28,230 --> 00:01:29,070
Behind the curtain.

29
00:01:32,150 --> 00:01:32,990
Coming.

30
00:01:34,510 --> 00:01:35,350
What is it?

31
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:36,600
It's important.

32
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,230
Why is it so dark here?

33
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,480
Open the curtains.

34
00:01:41,230 --> 00:01:42,070
Dad.

35
00:01:46,230 --> 00:01:47,070
I was mistaken.

36
00:01:47,310 --> 00:01:48,150
You...

37
00:01:51,230 --> 00:01:52,200
What is it? Spit it out.

38
00:01:52,870 --> 00:01:53,710
Lu Tingxiao,

39
00:01:53,870 --> 00:01:54,920
why check the ledgers?

40
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:57,040
My mom is the lady of Luzhou Group.

41
00:01:57,126 --> 00:01:58,235
You're just back from exile.

42
00:01:58,246 --> 00:01:59,710
Is it your place to point fingers?

43
00:02:00,150 --> 00:02:01,070
Lady of the Group?

44
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:03,000
Did your mom fund the Group,

45
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,510
or make some contributions?

46
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:06,200
I'm the CEO.

47
00:02:06,350 --> 00:02:07,790
Checking the ledgers is my duty.

48
00:02:08,310 --> 00:02:09,150
Besides,

49
00:02:09,590 --> 00:02:11,080
if she's done nothing wrong,

50
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:13,030
what's there to fear?

51
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,750
Don't twist the facts.

52
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,630
Instead of shouting at me here,

53
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,120
go and check the accounts,

54
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:19,800
and ask your mother about it.

55
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,430
Stop making a fool of yourself.

56
00:02:22,630 --> 00:02:23,470
Fine.

57
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,240
Just wait.

58
00:02:32,910 --> 00:02:33,750
Come out.

59
00:02:38,030 --> 00:02:39,400
Is that

60
00:02:39,590 --> 00:02:40,430
what you wanted

61
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,280
to report Xu Shulin about?

62
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,680
Ms. Xu,

63
00:02:50,691 --> 00:02:52,090
the Procurement Department under you

64
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,910
had a 50 million payment last month.

65
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,960
It was marked for building materials.

66
00:02:56,793 --> 00:02:57,800
But on the supplier list,

67
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,680
there's no matching transaction record.

68
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,630
That was for the specialty steel

69
00:03:01,641 --> 00:03:03,383
I set aside
for the Lianxin Island project.

70
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:06,190
The supplier is changing leadership,

71
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:08,560
so the paperwork isn't done yet.

72
00:03:09,310 --> 00:03:10,150
I see.

73
00:03:10,430 --> 00:03:11,310
I looked into it.

74
00:03:11,630 --> 00:03:14,000
The money went to a small company.

75
00:03:14,590 --> 00:03:17,520
The legal representative is Xu Wangzu.

76
00:03:18,930 --> 00:03:19,770
Xu Wangzu?

77
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,800
Ms. Xu's younger brother.

78
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:24,590
But that small company was struggling,

79
00:03:25,190 --> 00:03:27,310
and Xu Wangzu used the funds
to speculate on futures

80
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,360
and lost it all.

81
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,520
They're filing for bankruptcy.

82
00:03:33,136 --> 00:03:34,310
Lu Tingxiao, what do you mean?

83
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:36,800
Every cent will go where it should.

84
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,910
I'm a Vice President here.

85
00:03:39,310 --> 00:03:41,240
I can't even move funds now?

86
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:43,750
Ms. Xu,

87
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,430
we're talking about the facts.

88
00:03:46,550 --> 00:03:47,570
The Lianxin Island project

89
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,630
matters to Luzhou Group's future.

90
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,386
Raising funds hasn't been easy.

91
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,360
Any act of embezzlement

92
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,750
will not be tolerated.

93
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:58,030
Rules are for outsiders to see.

94
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:01,280
I'm the Chairman's wife.

95
00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:05,310
Your father's lawful wife.

96
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,000
According to the bylaws,

97
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:14,800
I propose

98
00:04:15,190 --> 00:04:16,800
we recover the 50 million at once

99
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:18,270
and suspend Xu Shulin

100
00:04:18,430 --> 00:04:20,240
from her Vice President post.

101
00:04:21,153 --> 00:04:22,453
Let's put it to a show of hands.

102
00:04:26,390 --> 00:04:27,240
Just you wait.

103
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,070
Lianxin Island needs massive funding.

104
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:34,240
Bank loans cover only 70%.

105
00:04:34,830 --> 00:04:36,390
A full 30%

106
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:37,600
came from private borrowing.

107
00:04:38,430 --> 00:04:39,270
That's way too risky.

108
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,390
If anything goes wrong,

109
00:04:40,783 --> 00:04:41,720
the cash flow will snap.

110
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:43,750
Put together

111
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,000
an investor list ASAP.

112
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:45,960
Yes, Mr. Lu.

113
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,580
(Miss Jiang, assistant)

114
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,720
Oh, and one more thing.

115
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,510
This morning,

116
00:04:50,620 --> 00:04:51,460
a flood of rumors

117
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,120
about your mother suddenly surfaced.

118
00:04:58,180 --> 00:04:59,580
(Lu Tingxiao's mom was a mistress)

119
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:05,580
(Scandal:
Lu Tingxiao's mom was a mistress)

120
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:09,180
(She died in guilt for embezzlement)

121
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,560
These rumors

122
00:05:11,630 --> 00:05:13,070
suddenly blew up online at noon.

123
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,920
The IP addresses were all hidden.

124
00:05:18,380 --> 00:05:20,180
(Scandal:
Lu Tingxiao's mom was a mistress)

125
00:05:26,540 --> 00:05:28,780
(Lianxin Island Fundraising Proposal)

126
00:05:34,070 --> 00:05:37,120
What kind of project is Lianxin Island?

127
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:40,190
Why does everyone want in?

128
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:48,560
Sis, look.

129
00:05:48,818 --> 00:05:49,795
Rumors about Fang Lanxin,

130
00:05:49,806 --> 00:05:51,630
the former lady of Luzhou Group.

131
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,560
Lu Tingxiao's mom?

132
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,320
Mom.

133
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,870
I miss you so much.

134
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:02,360
I really miss you.

135
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:06,480
Is Fang Lanxin really like that?

136
00:06:09,060 --> 00:06:12,340
(Fang Lanxin)

137
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:36,560
So, how is it?

138
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,120
Are you happy with the gift

139
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:39,790
I got for you?

140
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,200
Xu Shulin,

141
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,830
spreading lies about my mom,

142
00:06:44,270 --> 00:06:45,720
you've crossed my line.

143
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:49,000
Everything I said is true.

144
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,560
How is that spreading lies?

145
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,920
Your mom clawed her way up
as the mistress

146
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:54,950
and committed suicide.

147
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:56,560
Which part of that isn't true?

148
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,510
My mom was the lawful wife.

149
00:07:00,270 --> 00:07:01,190
You were the mistress.

150
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,390
You were behind the embezzlement.

151
00:07:04,630 --> 00:07:05,883
The Group got where it is today

152
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:07,920
thanks to my mom's side of the family.

153
00:07:08,430 --> 00:07:09,270
As for you,

154
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:10,270
since you married in,

155
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,600
you've been after my family's money.

156
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,750
You're just a parasite
living off my family.

157
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:15,880
How ungrateful

158
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,920
and disloyal.

159
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,560
Her family had power.

160
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,480
So what?

161
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,560
She was just a reckless spender

162
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:22,830
who ruined everything.

163
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,586
What makes her the lawful wife?

164
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:27,160
Your father and I grew up together.

165
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:28,360
We were engaged.

166
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:31,000
If she hadn't relied on her family

167
00:07:31,070 --> 00:07:31,920
and forced her way in,

168
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:35,160
I'd be the rightful lady of the family.

169
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,000
Your mom was the mistress.

170
00:07:37,270 --> 00:07:38,110
Shameless thing!

171
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,070
Say that again.

172
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,390
What's all this yelling?

173
00:07:46,630 --> 00:07:47,480
You're a mother,

174
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:49,070
yet your mouth is so filthy.

175
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:50,390
Have some dignity.

176
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,760
Jianchuan,

177
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:53,040
he started it.

178
00:07:53,190 --> 00:07:54,190
That's enough from you.

179
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:55,776
One more word and get out.

180
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,080
Tingxiao,

181
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,390
what you say and do now

182
00:08:05,950 --> 00:08:07,240
reflects the whole company.

183
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,040
Why argue with a woman?

184
00:08:09,870 --> 00:08:11,920
If word gets out, you'll be a joke.

185
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:14,120
She smeared my mom's name.

186
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,306
I can't pretend I didn't hear that.

187
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:17,960
Leave this matter

188
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:19,800
to me.

189
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:22,920
Right now, tell them

190
00:08:23,070 --> 00:08:24,190
to pull every report.

191
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,240
Don't let this blow up any further.

192
00:08:26,830 --> 00:08:27,670
Also,

193
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,273
reflect at home for three days.

194
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,750
Don't get involved in company matters.

195
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,040
That's not enough.

196
00:08:35,670 --> 00:08:37,550
I want her to apologize
to my mom in public.

197
00:08:45,670 --> 00:08:46,510
Tingxiao,

198
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:49,390
your mother passed away early.

199
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,360
I know how wronged you feel,

200
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:56,790
but this is a critical time
for the Lianxin Island project.

201
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:58,270
Stability comes first.

202
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,630
You're the CEO of the Group.

203
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,150
Think of the big picture.

204
00:09:02,870 --> 00:09:03,710
Let this matter

205
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:05,230
end here.

206
00:09:06,270 --> 00:09:07,270
Don't pursue further.

207
00:09:08,510 --> 00:09:09,350
Do you understand?

208
00:09:16,230 --> 00:09:17,080
Okay.

209
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:21,560
Good.

210
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:34,390
Everyone,

211
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:36,200
there have been a lot of rumors

212
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,320
about Luzhou Group's former CEO's wife,

213
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,600
Fang Lanxin,

214
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,473
saying she was a mistress,

215
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:43,910
stole company funds,
and committed suicide out of guilt.

216
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,910
But is that really the truth?

217
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:47,790
Fang came from a well-known family.

218
00:09:48,053 --> 00:09:49,416
She ignored her family's objections

219
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:51,120
and married

220
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,630
the then-broke Lu Jianchuan.

221
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:53,910
She used her dowry

222
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:55,720
to help him start up and expand,

223
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,790
and stood by him
through the hardest years.

224
00:09:58,030 --> 00:09:59,750
She was devoted to charity

225
00:09:59,816 --> 00:10:00,842
and kind to her employees.

226
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,870
Such a kind woman

227
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:04,510
was smeared as a mistress
and a big spender.

228
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,040
As a woman myself,

229
00:10:06,270 --> 00:10:07,600
I just can't let this slide.

230
00:10:08,270 --> 00:10:09,270
What can be verified is

231
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:10,790
that Lu Jianchuan

232
00:10:10,866 --> 00:10:12,349
brought back his new wife, Xu Shulin,

233
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:14,320
and his grade-school son

234
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:15,790
in less than a month

235
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,510
after Fang Lanxin died.

236
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:18,670
So, who was unfaithful?

237
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:19,670
Who was the mistress?

238
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:21,200
You can judge for yourselves.

239
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,510
Jin Chanchan is talking nonsense.

240
00:10:24,006 --> 00:10:25,172
She won't get away with this.

241
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,550
Find Lin Zhi'er's location now.

242
00:10:52,540 --> 00:10:54,980
(Followers)

243
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:59,910
Let's celebrate our 10M fans.

244
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,910
What are you doing here?

245
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:31,360
To see the top blogger shine.

246
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,240
I can't hear you.

247
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,000
Nothing. I just came to see you.

248
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,200
Enough talk. Dance with me.

249
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:40,230
Come on.

250
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:50,560
Dance with me.

251
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,160
I can't dance.

252
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:08,720
ظآزI forgot my umbrella in the rainظآز

253
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,700
ظآزThen I ran into youظآز

254
00:12:12,710 --> 00:12:15,940
ظآزWhen I'm hurt, sad, and fragileظآز

255
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:19,420
ظآزYou wrap me in your coatظآز

256
00:12:20,580 --> 00:12:24,040
ظآزBefore I knew it, I fell for youظآز

257
00:12:24,770 --> 00:12:28,160
ظآزWhen I'm upset, I think of youظآز

258
00:12:28,380 --> 00:12:32,040
ظآزYou somehow took overظآز

259
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:35,430
ظآزMy whole worldظآز

260
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:41,120
ظآزThank you for healing me with loveظآز

261
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:41,600
Come on.

262
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:44,820
ظآزHow can I ever repay youظآز

263
00:12:45,220 --> 00:12:49,070
ظآزMy eyes find you, softly and surelyظآز

264
00:12:49,250 --> 00:12:51,440
ظآزWe're meant to meetظآز

265
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,320
Why did you help me?

266
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,750
I just can't stand Xu Shulin.

267
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,670
So, I gave her a little trouble.

268
00:12:58,840 --> 00:12:59,680
I wasn't helping you.

269
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:02,870
That's not
like her good daughter-in-law,

270
00:13:03,510 --> 00:13:04,350
Zhi'er.

271
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:06,480
What you've been doing

272
00:13:06,550 --> 00:13:08,960
isn't like the obedient young master,

273
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:10,200
Tingxiao.

274
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:19,270
I haven't felt so relaxed in ages.

275
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:20,920
Yeah.

276
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:24,080
I wish time could stop right now.

277
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:30,910
Honey, it's been forever
since we danced.

278
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:31,920
Sure.

279
00:13:32,150 --> 00:13:33,600
Then let's dance all night.

280
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:34,590
Okay.

281
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,750
Do you want to run away with me,

282
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,440
Princess?

283
00:13:57,750 --> 00:14:02,390
ظآزLight through the mirror windowظآز

284
00:14:04,500 --> 00:14:09,090
ظآزA scent, like your faint outlineظآز

285
00:14:11,450 --> 00:14:17,290
ظآزHiding all the memories I knowظآز

286
00:14:17,580 --> 00:14:19,400
ظآزHow much hurt remainsظآز

287
00:14:19,730 --> 00:14:23,240
ظآزOnly I can savor itظآز

288
00:14:25,270 --> 00:14:31,200
ظآزAll I imagine for the futureظآز

289
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:37,440
ظآزHas you by my side in every sceneظآز

290
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:42,840
Mr. Lu,

291
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,630
that was

292
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,240
like we were running from a wedding.

293
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:50,280
Is that so?

294
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:52,750
There has to be a wedding first.

295
00:14:52,750 --> 00:14:58,630
ظآزNo need to care
or tell truth from liesظآز

296
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:05,810
ظآزWith you here, I fear nothing at allظآز

297
00:15:39,620 --> 00:15:41,070
ظآزThis doorظآز

298
00:15:41,470 --> 00:15:46,220
ظآزLets in the sky outsideظآز

299
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:50,260
ظآزWith a voice even lighterظآز

300
00:15:50,260 --> 00:15:53,070
ظآزThan how you just greeted meظآز

301
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:54,890
ظآزI know nowظآز

302
00:15:55,220 --> 00:16:00,100
ظآزWhat the chill in my body meansظآز

303
00:16:00,450 --> 00:16:03,320
ظآزThe moment salt hits the woundظآز

304
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:06,940
ظآزMy heart still beats so naivelyظآز

305
00:16:07,110 --> 00:16:10,100
ظآزTo completeظآز

306
00:16:10,560 --> 00:16:14,310
ظآزA joy that needs no brave pretenseظآز

307
00:16:14,450 --> 00:16:16,950
ظآزHow cruel sincerity can beظآز

308
00:16:17,090 --> 00:16:20,640
ظآزLike a door with no keyظآز

309
00:16:20,950 --> 00:16:23,270
ظآزMaybe you just passed byظآز

310
00:16:23,270 --> 00:16:26,850
ظآزThe tears in my eyesظآز

311
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:30,110
ظآزYou looked like you had nothing to sayظآز

312
00:16:30,110 --> 00:16:31,850
ظآزThen got so good at being coldظآز

313
00:16:31,850 --> 00:16:34,690
ظآزThat's why a smile feels so preciousظآز

314
00:16:34,900 --> 00:16:36,990
ظآزMaybe you just passed byظآز

315
00:16:37,140 --> 00:16:41,470
ظآزThe tears burned into my heartظآز

316
00:16:41,850 --> 00:16:44,140
ظآزLet's say silence was just for showظآز

317
00:16:44,140 --> 00:16:48,810
ظآزEven if I've grown another yearظآز
